b'At this unprecedented time, we\xe2\x80\x99re doing everything we can to continue to support you with the essentials you need. Here are some of the steps the Staples team is taking.
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
Community focus
We are currently prioritizing the needs of our customers who are on the front lines combatting the spread of COVID-19 for products that are essential, like hand sanitizer, masks, gloves and disinfectants. These customers include hospitals, first responders and long-term care facilities.\xc2\xa0We are urgently\xc2\xa0working with our suppliers to replenish our inventory and actively refreshing our sites so these products can be made available to all. \xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
\xe2\xa0\x80
Employee and customer safety
We have established new safety measures for our drivers\xc2\xa0including arming them with sanitizer, easing desktop drops when requested, and no longer requiring customers to sign for deliveries. \xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
Free delivery
Until further notice, we will provide free delivery on all orders and no minimum order size requirement. We ask that you consolidate orders when possible, as we strive to meet the needs of the maximum number of customers. \xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
In store
We\xe2\x80\x99ve reduced our Staples store hours, will close on Sundays and are offering curbside pickup, buy online pick up in store, and free Print & Marketing options if you don\xe2\x80\x99t have access to a printer and need to print takeout menus or school lessons for your children. We are continuing to stress the importance of social distancing with all customers and associates within our retail locations and will limit the number of customers in store.
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
Pricing update
We are committed to keeping our prices where they were before this crisis on categories essential to combatting COVID-19, and are partnering with our suppliers to provide you with the best prices possible.
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80
As an essential provider of business and educational materials and equipment, we will continue to be here for you through this difficult time. \xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80

Please note we are monitoring the COVID-19 situation daily, following guidance\xc2\xa0from the CDC and local, state\xc2\xa0and federal regulations, and will continue doing what\xe2\x80\x99s best for Staples customers and Staples associates.'
